name: ELEFANCLUB 03
description:
An original illustration for collectors (3+) of Les Elefants Terribles.

“Judy hosts a mythical polygon party for 39,
where albright screams yes it’s monkey tennis, you mother!
You had no right to condemn my spuds. 

But mister lonely night beak, with a jade green brilliant streak,
says some terribles are more elequal than others;
though it’s impossible to say which.

Yes your speciality might be wax cooties, 
but knives I can handle with a pulse.

So let them bleat rubber-time-negative-pizza cake…
but on the side, it’s a thing.”

Rotring pen and markers on paper

By Guillaume Cornet and Only Child No Pets
Follow @elefants_tez on twitter
